filmName: Star Wars: Episode IV - A New Hope
filmSummary: The plot follows the life of a simple farm boy, Luke Skywalker, as he and his newly met allies  attempt to rescue a Rebel leader, Princess Leia, from the clutches of the Empire.

filmName: Star Wars: Episode V - The Empire Strikes Back
filmSummary: Fleeing the evil Galactic Empire, the Rebels abandon their new base in an assault with the Imperial AT-AT walkers on the ice world of Hoth.

filmName: Star Wars: Episode VI - Return of the Jedi
filmSummary: Darth Vader and the Empire are building a new, indestructible Death Star.
